Subject: [PATCH] fbtft: add fb_ili9488 driver for ILI9488 LCD controller

Add support for ILI9488 TFT LCD controller with 18-bit color over SPI.
Based on driver from https://github.com/birdtechstep/fbtft-4.14

Upstream-Status: Pending

